🌋 Gorgoroth Testnet
Strong client diversity is essential for ETC. Gorgoroth provides a clean multi-client testnet for validating Type-2 (ECIP-1111) behavior across Fukuii, Core-Geth, and Besu. Solid step toward upcoming #EthereumClassic compatibility work. $ETC #ETC 💚